==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hurling
<hw>Hurl"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of throwing
with force.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of game at ball, formerly played.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Hurling</qex> taketh its denomination from throwing the
ball.</q> <rj><qau>Carew.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hurlwind</ent>⟦br⟧
